---
// Moment section - Minimal headline + stat with image
---

<section class="cre-moment-section">
  <div class="cre-moment-container">
    
    <!-- LEFT: FULL-HEIGHT IMAGE -->
    <div class="cre-moment-image">
      <img 
        src="/logos/intelio-website-pic-dashboard.webp" 
        alt="AI automation in financial services workflows"
        class="cre-moment-img"
      />
    </div>
    
    <!-- RIGHT: HEADLINE + STAT ONLY -->
    <div class="cre-moment-content">
      <h2 class="cre-moment-headline">
        The fastest financial services firms are automating analysisâ€”Why can't you?
      </h2>
      
      <p class="cre-moment-stat">
        Financial firms embedding AI into trading and analysis workflows execute <strong>50% faster</strong> and reduce analyst overhead by <strong>40%</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-moment-section {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #000000;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .cre-moment-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: stretch;
    min-height: 500px;
  }

  .cre-moment-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }

  .cre-moment-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .cre-moment-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: clamp(40px, 6vw, 60px);
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .cre-moment-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 32px 0;
    color: #000000;
  }

  .cre-moment-stat {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-moment-stat strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #000000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-moment-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      min-height: auto;
    }
    
    .cre-moment-image {
      height: 350px;
    }
    
    .cre-moment-content {
      padding: clamp(30px, 6vw, 50px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-moment-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .cre-moment-image {
      height: 280px;
    }
    
    .cre-moment-content {
      padding: clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px);
    }
    
    .cre-moment-headline {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .cre-moment-stat {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>

